 
<p>
The numbers of tourists now going to the main destinations are not only
making them unpleasant places to be, but also
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2023/apr/22/as-la-dolce-vita-turns-sour-thanks-to-overtourism-hotspots-are-turning-away-their-visitors">converting them</a>
into theme parks.

